パッケージ jp.summit_tech.domain.model

クラス Link

Object
Link
public class Link
extends Object
Model for link data. This is about any one project.

  • コンストラクタの詳細

    • Link

      public Link()
      Default constructor (default id and no is -1)

    • Link

      public Link​(long id)
      Constructor Used when only the id is known, such as when deleting.
      パラメータ:
      id - Id of this link data

    • Link

      public Link​(long id, long projectId, long sortNo, String url, String displayName, boolean thumbnailFlag, String thumbnailFileName, String thumbnailFilePath, MultipartFile upload)
      Constructor to set all items.
      パラメータ:
      id - Id of this link data
      projectId - Id of the project which owns this link data.
      sortNo - Sort order of this link on the page
      url - URL of this link
      displayName - The name used when this link data is published
      thumbnailFlag - If this flag is true, then thumbnail image uploaded by user is used, when this link published
      thumbnailFileName - The name of thumbnail image of this link (used only when thumbnailFlag is True)
      thumbnailFilePath - The saved path of thumbnail image of this link
      upload - Thumbnail image data (used only when uploading)
